    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a Lower Pleistocene cultural period preceding the Abbevillian. It is characterized by crudely flaked stone axes and beaked and keeled flint or stone objects.</Note_Text>
